lead_paragraph: Rafa Cabrera Bello rolled in a long birdie putt on the 18th hole to give Spain a one-shot lead after the opening round of foursomes at the World Cup of Golf in Melbourne on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Spain on Top of World Cup of Golf After First Round
